title: AVENGER 1.059 new 0106 FULL DATABASE PACK - APP with ALL SERIALs
description:
Do you remember S2k or better yet Oscar?

Avenger is Oscar's predessor with a bit of s2k rolled into it.

It contains over 70,000 serials and has the ability to make pre-loaded fixes/regg and cracks right on your desktop.

Some AV's complain about it's crack making abilities and it is a false postive. Avenger can still run if you choose to delete the component but it will also lose it's fix making abilities.

Monthly updates + more info for it can be found here http://S2k-Avenger.forever.as
